{"tid":881240,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬1：5負巴塞 拉莫斯：戰績決定盧比迪古命運","createTime":"2018-10-29T09:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T01:54:20.000Z","uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ca557d9d84e9cfbfa97baeaa9bfa8dd0d1d92f57","tid":881240,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"巴塞今場先有古天奴開齋加上蘇亞雷斯12碼，半場領先2：0。下半場皇馬一度由馬些路51分鐘追近1：2，不過蘇亞雷斯其後再入兩球，加上維達爾後備上陣頂入5：1，令皇馬大敗一場。<br />\n<br />\n輸波之後皇馬在西甲3連敗，拉莫斯說盧比迪古的命運是由成績決定：「成績決定一切。教練的命運不是球員決定，我們只能等待看有什麼變化出現。」<br />\n<br />\n相關內容<br />\n拉莫斯指皇馬不應該胡亂炒掉盧比迪古<br />\n盧柏迪古自責 拉莫斯：談易帥太瘋狂"},{"pid":"9230702cc65143294f9dd2b7c3787b67cd6949af","tid":881240,"uid":122233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯 = 政治家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2df30e0184e7e4e4089286b32d1eb5b6deed31a","tid":881240,"uid":54427,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"有球靚控助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a8a18c45cd9af90fc2cc5a98dc7ce9b9e99b5b","tid":881240,"uid":83094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:35:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"709350b18a1c26d33fb21423b0eb81debf749ade","tid":881240,"uid":3929,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"唔知以為拉狗宜家退左休做講波佬 好似琴晚場波佢冇份踢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49133a6e2f611102c20422832273ac8bcdc6f5c9","tid":881240,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"709350b18a1c26d33fb21423b0eb81debf749ade","tid":881240,"uid":3929,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,